ug-cookies/#breadcrumb"},"mainEntity":[{"@id":"https://blogghetti.com/nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies/#faq-question-1769619071846"},{"@id":"https://blogghetti.com/nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies/#faq-question-1769619486327"},{"@id":"https://blogghetti.com/nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies/#faq-question-1769619536234"}],"inLanguage":"en-US","potentialAction":[{"@type":"ReadAction","target":["https://blogghetti.com/nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies/"]}]},{"@type":"ImageObject","inLanguage":"en-US","@id":"https://blogghetti.com/nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies/#primaryimage","url":"https://blogghetti.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/feature-image-for-nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies.jpg","contentUrl":"https://blogghetti.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/feature-image-for-nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies.jpg","width":1200,"height":1200,"caption":"The primary feature image showing a festive spread of six Nutter Butter love bug cookies with pink sprinkles and heart accents on a tissue paper background.,"},{"@type":"BreadcrumbList","@id":"https://blogghetti.com/nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies/#breadcrumb","itemListElement":[{"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"name":"Home","item":"https://blogghetti.com/"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":2,"name":"Holidays","item":"https://blogghetti.com/category/holidays/"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":3,"name":"Valentine's Day","item":"https://blogghetti.com/category/holidays/valentines-day-sweet-treats/"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":4,"name":"Nutter Butter Love Bug Cookies"}]},{"@type":"WebSite","@id":"https://blogghetti.com/#website","url":"https://blogghetti.com/","name":"Blogghetti","description":"Simple and Delicious Recipes for Everyone","publisher":{"@id":"https://blogghetti.com/#/schema/person/d329c68cf3ac096325b73cfd5ea525bd"},"potentialAction":[{"@type":"SearchAction","target":{"@type":"EntryPoint","urlTemplate":"https://blogghetti.com/?s={search_term_string}"},"query-input":{"@type":"PropertyValueSpecification","valueRequired":true,"valueName":"search_term_string"}}],"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":["Person","Organization"],"@id":"https://blogghetti.com/#/schema/person/d329c68cf3ac096325b73cfd5ea525bd","name":"Lisa Kerhin","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","inLanguage":"en-US","@id":"https://blogghetti.com/#/schema/person/image/","url":"https://blogghetti.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/blogghetti-logo.png","contentUrl":"https://blogghetti.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/blogghetti-logo.png","width":500,"height":242,"caption":"Lisa Kerhin"},"logo":{"@id":"https://blogghetti.com/#/schema/person/image/"},"sameAs":["https://www.blogghetti.com/about"],"url":"https://blogghetti.com/author/blogging/"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://blogghetti.com/nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies/#faq-question-1769619071846","position":1,"url":"https://blogghetti.com/nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies/#faq-question-1769619071846","name":"What if I don’t have all the candy decorations?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"No problem! You can swap in similar candies, chocolate chips, or even mini marshmallows. Creativity is part of the fun, and each love bug will have its own personality.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://blogghetti.com/nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies/#faq-question-1769619486327","position":2,"url":"https://blogghetti.com/nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies/#faq-question-1769619486327","name":"Can kids help make them?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Absolutely. Kids can add sprinkles, place the eyes, and decorate the little love bugs. An adult should handle the melted candy to keep things safe.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://blogghetti.com/nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies/#faq-question-1769619536234","position":3,"url":"https://blogghetti.com/nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies/#faq-question-1769619536234","name":"Do the nutter butters need to be refrigerated?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Refrigeration isn’t necessary and can sometimes create condensation on the candy coating. Room temperature storage in a cool, dry spot works best to keep them looking their best.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Recipe","name":"Nutter Butter Love Bug Cookies","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Lisa Kerhin"},"description":"Love Bug Cookies are a cute no-bake peanut butter treat recipe made with candy melts and simple decorations that are fun to assemble and easy to share.","datePublished":"2026-01-28T16:45:15+00:00","image":["https://blogghetti.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/feature-image-for-nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies.jpg","https://blogghetti.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/feature-image-for-nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies-500x500.jpg","https://blogghetti.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/feature-image-for-nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies-500x375.jpg","https://blogghetti.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/feature-image-for-nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies-480x270.jpg"],"recipeYield":["6","6 cookies"],"prepTime":"PT30M","totalTime":"PT30M","recipeIngredient":["12  Nutter Butter Cookies","1 cup white candy melts","1 cup  pink candy melts","2 teaspoons red, white, and pink sprinkles","6  pretzel sticks, broken in half","12  edible candy eyes","6  mini chocolate chips","6  pink M&amp;Ms","6  jumbo red hearts sprinkles"],"recipeInstructions":[{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Tip: work in small batches so the candy melts stay easy to handle.","name":"Tip: work in small batches so the candy melts stay easy to handle.","url":"https://blogghetti.com/nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies/#wprm-recipe-165476-step-0-0"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Prepare your workspace: Line a baking sheet or tray with parchment paper to keep cookies from sticking and make cleanup easier.","name":"Prepare your workspace: Line a baking sheet or tray with parchment paper to keep cookies from sticking and make cleanup easier.","url":"https://blogghetti.com/nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies/#wprm-recipe-165476-step-0-1"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Melt the candy melts: In separate microwave-safe bowls, melt the pink and white candy melts in 30-second intervals, stirring in between until smooth.","name":"Melt the candy melts: In separate microwave-safe bowls, melt the pink and white candy melts in 30-second intervals, stirring in between until smooth.","url":"https://blogghetti.com/nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies/#wprm-recipe-165476-step-0-2"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Coat the cookies: Dip one completely in pink candy melts, tap off excess, and place on the parchment. Sprinkle the sides with red, white, and pink sprinkles, leaving the center clear for stacking.","name":"Coat the cookies: Dip one completely in pink candy melts, tap off excess, and place on the parchment. Sprinkle the sides with red, white, and pink sprinkles, leaving the center clear for stacking.","url":"https://blogghetti.com/nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies/#wprm-recipe-165476-step-0-3"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Assemble the body: Coat another cookie in white candy melts and gently place it crosswise on top of the pink-coated one to create the “love bug” body. Press lightly so it sticks without breaking.","name":"Assemble the body: Coat another cookie in white candy melts and gently place it crosswise on top of the pink-coated one to create the “love bug” body. Press lightly so it sticks without breaking.","url":"https://blogghetti.com/nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies/#wprm-recipe-165476-step-0-4"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Add the finishing touches: Insert pretzel halves for antennae, place candy eyes above a mini chocolate chip nose, and add pink M&amp;Ms or heart sprinkles near the bottom for accents.","name":"Add the finishing touches: Insert pretzel halves for antennae, place candy eyes above a mini chocolate chip nose, and add pink M&amp;Ms or heart sprinkles near the bottom for accents.","url":"https://blogghetti.com/nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies/#wprm-recipe-165476-step-0-5"}],"recipeCategory":["Dessert"],"recipeCuisine":["American"],"keywords":"love bug cookies, nutter butter cookies","@id":"https://blogghetti.com/nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies/#recipe","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://blogghetti.com/nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies/#article"},"mainEntityOfPage":"https://blogghetti.com/nutter-butter-love-bug-cookies/"}]}</script>
	<!-- / Yoast SEO Premium plugin. -->


